> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:59:04.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40eb9a0136b52de53a7631409a01f8aa5ba19b2","tid":876752,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:59:56.000Z","msg":"D門變上下閂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b989e6f0de47766827cb3063ebfb97022d74bd","tid":876752,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":34,"score":-34,"quote":{"pid":"e7bcb7ff8f64388078de7ba6bbb762f2eef9129d","tid":876752,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T00:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2013075/org/8f35d815e25ea9c235d143d75fc421f5.jpg/fki31yduUNRgvtMXM-XH-IfAyGqnSwhaCZ7VIwme1SM?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2013075%2Forg%2F8f35d815e25ea9c235d143d75fc421f5.jpg%2Ffki31yduUNRgvtMXM-XH-IfAyGqnSwhaCZ7VIwme1SM%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=023c7fb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n常有人搭港鐵時自以為身手不凡，愛在最後一刻衝上車，有網民近日目擊有抱着嬰兒的心急父母，在金鐘站衝門失敗，反而其嬰兒車卻成功達陣，門一關上，徒留嬰兒車留在車門前，令其他乘客大為愕然。最終有好心乘客在下站推出嬰兒車交職員處理。不少網民看到照片後笑爆，直指幸BB不在車上，又齊齊分享曾目擊的地鐵衝門騎呢事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2011325/org/ed34499be219f173927efba6708695a5.jpg/Ww6VwajIuYM7_tCxiiTMiJsEzjO99ajjRtWxVkbVsVY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2011325%2Forg%2Fed34499be219f173927efba6708695a5.jpg%2FWw6VwajIuYM7_tCxiiTMiJsEzjO99ajjRtWxVkbVsVY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=21b7909c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日有網民就目擊到一對父母抱着嬰兒在金鐘站想衝車但失敗，反而他們的嬰兒車就成功達陣。(fb用戶「Jason Kong」圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2012053/org/e53bb18e7442d75c59104e5f322b0278.JPG/rGwiTmiH5zxGwLRm_QFlgromc--HeQU_eaF8yXmhfMk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2012053%2Forg%2Fe53bb18e7442d75c59104e5f322b0278.JPG%2FrGwiTmiH5zxGwLRm_QFlgromc--HeQU_eaF8yXmhfMk&h=e484ca64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2012056/org/406f28b29dc82db83d6a4d752c9354c1.JPG/Dz7xN0PXf0kI4huACir4bfMKqlJm8SLdVvyn0Vb8p9E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2012056%2Forg%2F406f28b29dc82db83d6a4d752c9354c1.JPG%2FDz7xN0PXf0kI4huACir4bfMKqlJm8SLdVvyn0Vb8p9E&h=f92d2c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2012051/org/35dfd1bfc3189c1a7439f5e183b7017d.JPG/9gFUX6sYf6YZxN3aJ2uEWsvtwJNDvcySGeypzRnsqc0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2012051%2Forg%2F35dfd1bfc3189c1a7439f5e183b7017d.JPG%2F9gFUX6sYf6YZxN3aJ2uEWsvtwJNDvcySGeypzRnsqc0&h=f1e8201b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2012054/org/1ee83521d941b343e0a6458407b5ca57.JPG/HWoeSoOk6jt4awS1BbdK1llfPt4HKeC91NteiNTbXog\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2012054%2Forg%2F1ee83521d941b343e0a6458407b5ca57.JPG%2FHWoeSoOk6jt4awS1BbdK1llfPt4HKeC91NteiNTbXog&h=78932f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2012052/org/a2d458e7cdf15c23561d463369d0a593.JPG/zjzeloE0tjtaWhl_VheeCnHOXW951w-f8aaP_fGmj_0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2012052%2Forg%2Fa2d458e7cdf15c23561d463369d0a593.JPG%2FzjzeloE0tjtaWhl_VheeCnHOXW951w-f8aaP_fGmj_0&h=e9b2acf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2012058/org/b7242271037dee1009ceff610557dac6.JPG/SSH6C0y7Pqmr_7wqdW9HSJcTwuJO7aAOSbmJ0Em5idA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2012058%2Forg%2Fb7242271037dee1009ceff610557dac6.JPG%2FSSH6C0y7Pqmr_7wqdW9HSJcTwuJO7aAOSbmJ0Em5idA&h=f1db39b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2012057/org/110efa791869a1591713952d829320bb.JPG/hSh_KTZn4OWCRUuE0E8tjINVA3NbDFx7d1FeLHdRXiw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2012057%2Forg%2F110efa791869a1591713952d829320bb.JPG%2FhSh_KTZn4OWCRUuE0E8tjINVA3NbDFx7d1FeLHdRXiw&h=164c3309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少網民都直言父母疏忽安全，為嬰兒甚至他人帶來危險。(fb群組「西環變幻時」截圖）<br />\n<br />\n對於有乘客在金鐘站衝門時，僅得BB車進入車廂事件，港鐵回覆《香港01》時指出，昨晚約7時，有職員接獲一對男女乘客求助，稱乘搭往荃灣方向列車時，在近車尾位置遺失一架嬰兒車，其後一名乘客在尖沙嘴站向職員稱拾獲該架嬰兒車，職員隨即聯絡失主取回。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵呼籲乘客上落車時注意安全，當車門或幕門正在關閉時，切勿嘗試進入車廂，並要小心保管財物。<br />\n<br />\n有網民在昨晚(24日)約7時搭港鐵荃灣線時目擊一件奇事，當時他站在近車門位置並正往荃灣方向。列車到達金鐘站時，目擊一對抱B父母在月台衝上車，就快關門一刻，嬰兒車被他們成功推入車廂，惟他們一家3口卻仍留在原地，只能目送列車帶着其嬰兒車開出。<br />\n<br />\n樓主指全車目擊事件的乘客，大感愕然，望着與物主「失散」的可憐嬰兒車，哭笑不得，大家都慶幸車上沒有嬰兒。樓主透露後來有乘客仗義幫忙，於尖沙咀站下車時，順道推嬰兒車出車廂找職員處理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2013053/org/f0fbf3cda20fd165845682b0617b8e31.jpg/HU_3NBL3NWZAPtaFBjG2qgsQhOZG1Oc5liUi15YlItc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2013053%2Forg%2Ff0fbf3cda20fd165845682b0617b8e31.jpg%2FHU_3NBL3NWZAPtaFBjG2qgsQhOZG1Oc5liUi15YlItc&h=f9daa6a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不時有網民分享乘客衝門失敗狼狽事件，網上流傳疑似菠蘿包夾車門而物主未能上車的照片。(fb群組「西環變幻時」截圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2012856/org/63ba1224a1fae38bcd2acad71a362ab0.jpg/dgWIiKa52aBdWwK9WHZiFU2IjHt_Solp3Kc2sdynNrE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2012856%2Forg%2F63ba1224a1fae38bcd2acad71a362ab0.jpg%2FdgWIiKa52aBdWwK9WHZiFU2IjHt_Solp3Kc2sdynNrE&h=3a628d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前有男子被拍到以雙手推港鐵幕門，被批自私，網民後來改圖把他變成摩西，笑他試渡紅海。（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2012867/org/2243e7c76257fcfa28b10d75253429f1.jpg/Dh6kNfjqBc0S8ktWoNnahnOoteSfQZHAcajVGXGo1Rk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2012867%2Forg%2F2243e7c76257fcfa28b10d75253429f1.jpg%2FDh6kNfjqBc0S8ktWoNnahnOoteSfQZHAcajVGXGo1Rk&h=0de864e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過去曾有網民目擊者衝門者未及收遮事件，十分爆笑。（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2012873/org/b151eb3950c73561f508c97beed8d37c.jpg/KzgKOcMuwbHEF8i3Jjdr3mXnbUAIBUQk38kqKN_JKig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2012873%2Forg%2Fb151eb3950c73561f508c97beed8d37c.jpg%2FKzgKOcMuwbHEF8i3Jjdr3mXnbUAIBUQk38kqKN_JKig&h=e813a6eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年初一名中年漢手持膠袋卡在一班東鐵紅磡站的列車車門，需由職員協助取出，被其他乘客踢爆衝門，其間更向職員爆粗。<br />\n<br />\n這張「孤獨嬰兒車」照片被樓主上載到facebook，他留言感慨「點解要衝閘呢？係咪衰，而家架BB車上左車，但係個人上唔到。」其他網民亦熱烈回應，有人直言該對父母忽視安全，為嬰兒甚至他人帶來危險，「 推住bb車就跟本唔應該衝！」、「愈論盡嘅人愈鐘意衝門」。有人更稱應要給父母教訓，「由得佢，自己去到尾站重逢架車！」<br />\n<br />\n其實不時都有網民分享部份乘客因衝車門失敗而發生的狼狽事件，例如車門夾菠蘿包、夾頭髮，有人成功上車但就遺留了背囊在外，有人愛以身體各部位擋門博車門重開，除以手腳以外，甚至有人以跑手衝線時的「壓線」方式以頭擋門，縱成功令車門彈開，頭部兩側也十分痛，上月更曾有母親因衝車門而導致夾手指。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/250999/%E5%BF%83%E6%80%A5%E7%88%B8%E5%AA%BD%E8%A1%9D%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97-%E5%83%85bb%E8%BB%8A%E5%AD%A4%E7%8D%A8%E9%81%94%E9%99%A3-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E9%96%8B%E5%BF%83share%E8%A1%9D%E9%96%80%E9%A8%8E%E5%91%A2%E4%BA%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F250999%2F%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2580%25A5%25E7%2588%25B8%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E8%25A1%259D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2595%2597-%25E5%2583%2585bb%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25AD%25A4%25E7%258D%25A8%25E9%2581%2594%25E9%2599%25A3-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25BF%2583share%25E8%25A1%259D%25E9%2596%2580%25E9%25A8%258E%25E5%2591%25A2%25E4%25BA%258B&d=mmcIkk46CeecWPKyTqT64DQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=554b7534\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/250999/%E5%BF%83%E6%80%A5%E7%88%B8%E5%AA%BD%E8%A1%9D%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97-%E5%83%85bb%E8%BB%8A%E5%AD%A4%E7%8D%A8%E9%81%94%E9%99%A3-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E9%96%8B%E5%BF%83share%E8%A1%9D%E9%96%80%E9%A8%8E%E5%91%A2%E4%BA%8B</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:00:14.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦<br />\n由得架車自己送到入廠"},{"pid":"f883a4ada7db275c3e70c30f4a359fd4f9d97d6d","tid":876752,"uid":74698,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:01:24.000Z","msg":"之前見過有個啊媽淨係推咗架有BB嘅BB車上車自己冇上到<br />\n一閂埋門成車人o撚晒咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e41fc74ffad2b28993756f57153a0f2d74173f","tid":876752,"uid":80103,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:13:27.000Z","msg":"呢啲父母咪撚生仔啦<br />\n<br />\n平時見啲家長用個五六歲既細路推入去<br />\n<br />\n知我地驚整親佢讓開 但我次次都企直頂撚住佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14da3377c32dbab52a7a30fa0db5d21162de4454","tid":876752,"uid":75802,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/151342_fa2375cb88179a27d93377778c8065fa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F151342_fa2375cb88179a27d93377778c8065fa.png&h=0b851ff7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c9467cddf15eaacc6df16885bb7b1a2561ec4d8","tid":876752,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:15:11.000Z","msg":"唔收車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好撚冇公德心"},{"pid":"fb10910a1d34621b544bd70f14a5b26dc1423098","tid":876752,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14da3377c32dbab52a7a30fa0db5d21162de4454","tid":876752,"uid":75802,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018